WEBVTT

04:13.754 --> 04:15.756
No, nothing.

04:17.007 --> 04:19.051
- Really?
- Yes!

04:50.165 --> 04:52.167
Hey, wombie.

04:52.251 --> 04:54.420
Have you seen my score
for the Saint-Saëns?

04:54.503 --> 04:55.796
It's not in my folder.

04:55.879 --> 04:57.756
Why would I know
where your music is?

04:57.840 --> 04:59.633
I don't know.

04:59.717 --> 05:02.469
Sorry for daring
to ask a question.

05:02.553 --> 05:03.887
Are you done?

05:03.971 --> 05:06.348
I need to borrow your phones.
Mine are fucked.

05:06.432 --> 05:09.768
Not like I'm getting
anything done anyways.

05:09.852 --> 05:13.313
You know what they say.

05:13.397 --> 05:16.316
"Whoo-hoo. Spring break."

05:16.400 --> 05:18.152
I'll be in my room.

05:18.235 --> 05:21.071
Welcome.

05:21.155 --> 05:22.531
No, no, no, wait.
You have to go north.

05:22.614 --> 05:23.657
They have these
amazing vineyards.

05:23.741 --> 05:24.950
It's, like, this wine country...

05:25.034 --> 05:26.285
Mm-hmm, yeah.

05:26.368 --> 05:28.037
Uh, right next to Venice.
What's it called?

05:28.120 --> 05:29.788
- The Veneto.
- Well, that is an option.

05:29.872 --> 05:31.457
- That's an option.
<i>- Il Veneto.</i>

05:31.540 --> 05:34.043
You got to get it right. Yes.

05:35.335 --> 05:37.629
Oh, hey.

05:37.713 --> 05:40.799
Juju, sweetheart, you girls
finished practice already?

05:40.883 --> 05:42.259
Uh, Vi's still going.

05:42.342 --> 05:43.594
