05:43.677 --> 05:45.054
Oh, I thought you had twins.

05:45.137 --> 05:46.388
Two minutes apart.

05:46.472 --> 05:48.182
Someone has to hold the door.
Right?

05:49.558 --> 05:51.351
But we heard your news.
Juilliard.

05:51.435 --> 05:53.187
Congrats. That's incredible.

05:53.270 --> 05:55.564
Uh, you're thinking
of my sister Vi.

05:55.647 --> 05:57.316
She's going to Juilliard
next year.

05:57.399 --> 05:59.234
Julie is taking the gap year
to consider her options.

05:59.318 --> 06:01.695
That's smart.
You know what, I have a cousin.

06:01.779 --> 06:03.238
He did fine arts,
college, everything.

06:03.322 --> 06:05.449
Eight years later,
he's teaching preschoolers

06:05.532 --> 06:07.826
how to make things out of
<i>washi</i> tape. - Hey.

06:07.910 --> 06:09.369
-Crafts are important.
-I'm just saying,

06:09.453 --> 06:10.662
there's eight billion people
on this planet,

06:10.746 --> 06:12.206
and everybody wants to have

06:12.289 --> 06:13.999
their moment in the spotlight,
and it's not gonna happen.

06:14.083 --> 06:15.584
The Instagram generation
needs to be more realistic

06:15.667 --> 06:17.961
about long-term
career prospects.

06:18.045 --> 06:21.006
I don't have social media, so...

06:21.090 --> 06:22.132
- See?
- Oh, good.

06:22.216 --> 06:23.217
That's a start.

06:23.300 --> 06:24.927
Dad, what time
are we leaving tomorrow?

06:25.010 --> 06:26.637
-Oh, whenever you want.
-They're at boarding school.

06:26.720 --> 06:28.889
- Lindberg Academy.
- The arts school?

06:28.972 --> 06:30.516
Isn't that where that girl...?

06:32.101 --> 06:33.519
It's fine.

06:33.602 --> 06:35.270
I didn't really know her.

06:38.065 --> 06:39.650
Okay, hey, sweetie,
make sure you got

06:39.733 --> 06:40.943
everything ready for tomorrow.

06:41.026 --> 06:42.194
Okay.

06:42.277 --> 06:43.654
- Nice to meet you.
- Bye, guys.

06:45.030 --> 06:47.116
Um... okay.

06:47.199 --> 06:49.159
So, what was...
I'm sorry, what was that place?

07:30.409 --> 07:33.036
Max! Max!

07:33.120 --> 07:34.955
-Hi.
-Hey, Vi.

07:37.082 --> 07:38.667
Yeah, no problem, Vi!

07:38.750 --> 07:40.085
Just take your time!

07:40.169 --> 07:41.879
Car will unload itself!

07:41.962 --> 07:43.255
Young love.

07:43.338 --> 07:44.840
A father's waking nightmare.

07:44.923 --> 07:46.258
You got your pills?

07:46.341 --> 07:47.718
All right, look.

07:47.801 --> 07:49.469
I know the Juilliard thing
hit you hard.

07:49.553 --> 07:51.180
And they don't know
what they're missing.

07:51.263 --> 07:52.431
But no, listen to me.

07:52.514 --> 07:53.932
You got a big heart.

07:54.016 --> 07:55.934
You got a beautiful face.

07:56.018 --> 07:57.019
-Dad.
-And no matter what

07:57.102 --> 07:58.687
those artistes
in there tell you,

07:58.770 --> 08:01.231
there's more to life
than solos and spotlights.

08:01.315 --> 08:04.902
And any academic school
would kill to have you.

08:04.985 --> 08:07.112
All right, I'll get your stuff.

08:42.898 --> 08:46.193
Moira Wilson was one of
the finest musicians

08:46.276 --> 08:49.071
ever to grace Lindberg Academy.

08:49.154 --> 08:52.741
For many of you,
what happened here six weeks ago

08:52.824 --> 08:56.161
will be your first
experience of loss.

08:56.245 --> 08:58.747
Moira's passing
is a stark reminder

08:58.830 --> 09:00.499
of the darkness we all face

09:00.582 --> 09:04.878
in our lives
and in our artistic pursuits.

09:04.962 --> 09:08.590
As you all know, Moira was
to deliver the concerto solo

09:08.674 --> 09:11.343
in our Music Showcase
later this quarter.

09:11.426 --> 09:13.345
A long-standing
school tradition,

09:13.428 --> 09:15.764
the senior concerto
has successfully launched

09:15.847 --> 09:19.643
the careers of many Lindberg
graduates over the years.

09:19.726 --> 09:22.396
Following much discussion,
we have decided

09:22.479 --> 09:24.690
to rerun the senior
concerto competition

09:24.773 --> 09:27.234
in her memory.

09:27.317 --> 09:31.363
Music majors of all disciplines
are encouraged to participate.

09:31.446 --> 09:34.408
Submit your repertoire
to Dr. Cask.

10:28.503 --> 10:31.757
