11:44.746 --> 11:46.289
Oh, you know what I think.
Nobody...

11:46.373 --> 11:49.126
"No one ever won anything
with Mozart."

12:00.345 --> 12:02.931
Jules, I say this lovingly
as your sister:

12:03.014 --> 12:04.349
Grow some balls.

12:04.433 --> 12:05.976
Repeat after me:

12:06.059 --> 12:07.853
Roger Melling,
you are a drunken,

12:07.936 --> 12:09.729
cockless excuse of a teacher...

12:09.813 --> 12:12.607
-Okay, I can't actually
say that, though, can I? -Why?

12:12.691 --> 12:14.443
You're scared
he'll set the claw on you?

12:14.526 --> 12:16.111
Okay, stop.

12:16.194 --> 12:19.489
It's focal dystonia, and it's
common in musicians his age.

12:19.573 --> 12:21.867
The claw.
It's gonna get you.

12:27.122 --> 12:28.748
Hey, you dropped...

13:42.280 --> 13:43.573
Phrasing.

13:49.287 --> 13:51.831
Good. Very good.

13:51.915 --> 13:53.833
I see you managed
to fit in some practice

13:53.917 --> 13:56.628
between all the drugs
and the underage drinking.

13:56.711 --> 13:59.130
I leave the drinking
to the experts.

13:59.214 --> 14:00.924
Very funny.

14:02.509 --> 14:04.386
-They're rerunning the concerto.
-So I hear.

14:04.469 --> 14:05.971
Feeling positive?

14:06.054 --> 14:07.973
I was thinking about
changing my piece.

14:08.056 --> 14:10.850
I've been looking
at Saint-Saëns' 2.

14:10.934 --> 14:13.853
Third movement still needs work,
but I can get there.

14:13.937 --> 14:16.022
-You mean Vivian's piece?
-It's not that hard.

14:16.106 --> 14:17.774
Cask lets Vi play it.

14:17.857 --> 14:19.234
Henry's methods are his own.

14:19.317 --> 14:21.236
I know, but if I just
get the chance...

14:21.319 --> 14:23.905
You'd make a pig's ear of it.

14:23.989 --> 14:25.365
Is that what you want?

14:25.448 --> 14:28.868
Stick with Herr Amadeus.

14:28.952 --> 14:31.913
He will reward you.
He always does.

15:23.673 --> 15:25.383
Uh, Dr. Cask?

15:28.178 --> 15:30.221
