17:52.947 --> 17:56.117
"Immortal glory awaits she
who in her darkness welcomes me.

17:56.201 --> 17:59.120
"The path required
this book depicts:

17:59.204 --> 18:01.831
one, two, three,
four, five, six."

18:45.625 --> 18:47.544
Tartini.

18:50.380 --> 18:51.673
The composer.

18:51.756 --> 18:54.217
It didn't say the piece.

18:54.300 --> 18:56.135
That's the "Devil's Trill."

18:56.219 --> 18:58.513
By the way, Vivian doesn't know

18:58.596 --> 19:02.183
you're playing
the same piece as her, does she?

19:07.522 --> 19:09.899
